{"tid":943631,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"有冇人知近排電台成日播一首好好聽嘅歌叫咩名？","createTime":"2018-12-16T15:30:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T20:08:38.000Z","uid":9272,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7a9053744aca4969219c4bc481ca063572ddccfa","tid":943631,"uid":9272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T15:30:12.000Z","msg":"近一個月內搭小巴聽過幾次<br />\n<br />\n男人唱，廣東歌<br />\n<br />\n唔知邊間電台，連歌詞一句都唔鬼記得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n已經喺各大電台/音樂平台搵左好耐，都搵唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇心水推介 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320ac6f5c893a9be810b70b6a704dbd73d4f8894","tid":943631,"uid":9272,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T15:35:50.000Z","msg":"已知唔係 叱咤我最喜愛歌曲頭15位，以及以下嘅歌：<br />\n1. 為全世界歌唱 - 鄭欣宜/AGA/周柏豪/胡鴻鈞/梁釗峰/陳柏宇/Gin Lee/JW/許廷鏗/吳業坤<br />\n2. 身體語言 - Dear Jane ft. Miss Janni<br />\n3. 但願人長久 - Hana菊梓喬<br />\n4. 在月台上等你 - 衛蘭<br />\n5. My Love - 劉德華<br />\n6. 揮揮手 - JW<br />\n7. 笑容迷路了 - 黃妍<br />\n8. 廢青 - 譚詠麟<br />\n9.  白紙 - 許廷鏗<br />\n10. 龍舌蘭 - 陳奕迅<br />\n11. 生之頌 - 林奕匡<br />\n12. 偉業街 - 胡鴻鈞<br />\n13. 太空艙 - 古巨基<br />\n14. 重陽 - 鄧小巧<br />\n15. Time to Go - 岑日珈<br />\n16. 阿龍理髮 - 劉浩龍<br />\n17. 風靡 - Gin Lee<br />\n18. 大不了一代 - Nowhere Boys<br />\n19. 殘缺的彩虹 - 陳綺貞<br />\n20. 掉進海的眼淚 - 洪嘉豪"},{"pid":"e7861d2d7fa5646bea4cd1274a24b0f88cac2f46","tid":943631,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T15:40:46.000Z","msg":"郭富城 - 弱"},{"pid":"3a23100ecbf7760cd3e6e837c8eda04fde7b756a","tid":943631,"uid":56240,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e7861d2d7fa5646bea4cd1274a24b0f88cac2f46","tid":943631,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T15:40:46.000Z","msg":"郭富城 - 弱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T15:42:06.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"0f63b14bdd196f5be23496ba113a4f318ff4fb82","tid":943631,"uid":331